The paper deals with a problem of assigning students to projects, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.DS). The use of network flows and matching algorithms suggests that the paper may also be relevant to game theory (cs.GT) and graph theory (cs.LG).
